001package com.telos.loops.contacts;
002
003import com.fasterxml.jackson.annotation.JsonIgnoreProperties;
004
005/**
006 * Request to delete a contact from Loops.
007 *
008 * <p>You must provide either an email address or a userId to identify the contact to delete.
009 * Providing both is allowed but not required.
010 *
011 * @param email the email address of the contact to delete
012 * @param userId your application's unique identifier for the contact to delete
013 */
014@JsonIgnoreProperties(ignoreUnknown = false)
015public record ContactDeleteRequest(String email, String userId) {}
